text: Bailaho is a brand for a German-language business directory for the business- to-business sector. Trademark owner is the company Bailaho GmbH based in Baden-Baden in Germany.German Trademark Register German Patent and Trade Mark OfficeTrademark Register European Union Intellectual Property Office The brand has been on the market in Germany, Austria and Switzerland since 2011. == References == == External links == * Official Website Bailaho Germany * Official Website Bailaho Austria * Official Website Bailaho Switzerland Category:German brands Category:Trademarks Category:Directories
